{"tid":2354194,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"KIA(起亞) 將會在2021年1月啟用全新的 LOGO","createTime":"2021-01-05T09:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T13:31:24.000Z","uid":109923,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6c67b1b0cda3d687e65f48b1412f5456c4bb7a0c","tid":2354194,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"有不少車企在近年來更換了新車標，新的車標可以適應新世代的審美、帶給消費者新的視覺形象。同時車企可以藉此機會給消費者宣傳新的品牌理念與發展方向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2w6b9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2w6b9q.jpg&h=56098296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新logo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bFe5uq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bFe5uq.png&h=a6fd2548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近期，有外媒報導，KIA(起亞) 將會在2021年1月啟用全新的 LOGO，替換掉 2012年至今的商標。相對於之前的橢圓形商標，新的設計突破了邊緣框框的限制，看起來更加具有時尚感與連貫性。有消息稱 KIA 已在最近向韓國專利局提交了新品牌 LOGO 的相關專利文件。"},{"pid":"0b84cbafd29573319c803151428cda74fa8dd23b","tid":2354194,"uid":91317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"F1?"},{"pid":"025c483a8d08bb1f63b8774e1b282216232fbf67","tid":2354194,"uid":66365,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"KN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aaa80771547fceb7ec63d48dca5d17e1927f18c","tid":2354194,"uid":294,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"7個logo 都奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd3bf07d3c5a0a8285a61267ab499146fc8b271","tid":2354194,"uid":339384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7bbe159a4f2df9ef8e1bd9dc8968d7c6443d98","tid":2354194,"uid":339384,"like"